packages.name: Microsoft WebView2
packages.description:
Publisher: Microsoft
Download: https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/webview2/#download-section
Supported Operating Systems: Windows 10, 11, Server 2016, 2019, 2022
Supported Architecture: 32/64 bit

Notes:
1. This is the WebView2 Evergreen Version and is designed to auto-update.
2. Error code -2147219187 means an existing or newer version of Webview2 is already installed. This has been added as a success code.
